Title: Frontend Developer
          Company: TechCorp
          Location: Bangalore, India
          Type: Full-time
          Salary: $80,000 - $100,000
          Skills: React, JavaScript, TypeScript, HTML, CSS
          Description: We are looking for a skilled Frontend Developer to join our team in Bangalore. You will be responsible for building user interfaces using React and ensuring responsive design across all devices. 3+ years of experience required.

Title: Senior Frontend Engineer
          Company: InnovateX
          Location: Bangalore, India
          Type: Full-time
          Salary: $110,000 - $130,000
          Skills: React, Redux, Next.js, TypeScript, Testing
          Description: InnovateX is seeking a Senior Frontend Engineer to lead our frontend development efforts. You'll work on complex web applications using modern JavaScript frameworks and collaborate with designers and backend engineers. 5+ years of experience required.

Title: UI/UX Developer
          Company: DesignWave
          Location: Bangalore, India
          Type: Full-time
          Salary: $90,000 - $110,000
          Skills: React, Figma, UI/UX Design, CSS, SASS
          Description: Join our creative team as a UI/UX Developer in our Bangalore office. You'll be working at the intersection of design and development, creating beautiful and functional user interfaces. Strong design sensibility and frontend coding skills required.

Title: Backend Developer
          Company: DataSystems
          Location: Bangalore, India
          Type: Full-time
          Salary: $85,000 - $105,000
          Skills: Node.js, Express, MongoDB, PostgreSQL
          Description: We're looking for a Backend Developer to build robust APIs and server-side applications. You'll work with our team in Bangalore to design and implement scalable backend solutions for our growing user base.

Title: Full Stack Developer
          Company: OmniTech
          Location: Bangalore, India
          Type: Full-time
          Salary: $95,000 - $120,000
          Skills: React, Node.js, MongoDB, AWS
          Description: OmniTech is hiring a Full Stack Developer for our Bangalore office. You'll be working on all aspects of our web application, from the frontend interface to the backend services. We're looking for someone who can handle the full development lifecycle.
